    Root cause: race condition between AuthProvider hydration and Mangaka
    mount. Multiple contributing factors:
    
    1. AuthProvider: loading initial state was false, so ProtectedRoute/
       HomeOrWorkspace rendered branches before sessionStorage was validated,
       causing flash + redirect loop. Now loading=true until useEffect
       hydrates, and validateSession() rejects corrupt/invalid sessions
       (missing token, unknown role) to avoid getRolePath returning wrong path.
    
    2. App.jsx HomeOrWorkspace: didn't check isLoggingIn, so Home could
       flash before Login's navigate took effect. Now waits for both
       loading and isLoggingIn to clear; fallback to /l